    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AllTablesImporter
    Central importer runner for loading all system tables from TXT files.
    BackgroundJobs
    Manages all background and scheduled jobs of the Bistro server.
    BillDAO
    Data Access Object (DAO) for handling billing operations.
    BillDAO.BillLookupResult
    Result wrapper for bill lookup operations.
    BillDAO.BillReminderRow
    Lightweight record used for reminder processing.
    BillDAO.PayBillResult
    Result wrapper for payment operations.
    BillDTO
    DTO representing a customer bill.
    BistroClient
    Client-side network component of the Bistro system.
    BistroServer
    Main OCSF server of the Bistro system.
    ClientConnectionRow
    Represents a single row in the server's client connections table.
    ClientController
    JavaFX controller for the Bistro client application.
    ClientFX
    Entry point of the Bistro Client application.
    ClientSession
    Manages the client-side session state for the Bistro application.
    ClientUI
    Defines the callback interface for client-side UI components.
    CurrentDinersDTO
    DTO representing a currently seated group in the restaurant.
    CurrentDinersRow
    Represents a single row in the "Current Diners" table.
    DatabaseResetter
    Utility class responsible for clearing all database tables before running data import processes.
    EmailService
    Utility service for sending system emails (reservation confirmations, reminders, waiting-list updates).
    Envelope
    A generic network wrapper used for all client-server communication.
    HistoryDTO
    DTO representing historical activity of a customer or subscriber.
    KryoMessage
    A lightweight transport wrapper used to send Kryo-serialized data between client and server.
    KryoUtil
    Utility class responsible for Kryo serialization and deserialization.
    LoginController
    JavaFX controller for the login screen.
    LoginRequestDTO
    DTO representing a login request sent from client to server.
    LoginResponseDTO
    DTO representing a login response sent from server to client.
    MakeReservationRequestDTO
    DTO representing a reservation creation request sent from client to server.
    MakeReservationResponseDTO
    DTO representing a response to a reservation creation or availability request.
    MySQLConnectionPool
    Singleton MySQL connection pool.
    OpCode
    Defines all operation codes used in client-server communication.
    OpeningHoursDAO
    Data Access Object for managing restaurant opening hours.
    OpeningHoursDTO
    DTO representing restaurant opening hours.
    PayBillController
    JavaFX controller for the "Pay Bill" screen.
    PerformanceLogDAO
    Data Access Object for performance and behavior logging.
    PooledConnection
    Creates a new pooled connection wrapper.
    ProfileDTO
    DTO representing a subscriber profile.
    RegistrationDTO
    DTO used for subscriber registration.
    ReportDAO
    Data Access Object for generating management reports.
    ReportDTO
    DTO used for reporting and statistics.
    ReportRequestDTO
    DTO used to request a monthly report from the server.
    Reservation
    Entity that matches table: reservation Columns: - reservation_id - num_of_customers - reservation_time - expiry_time - status - confirmation_code
    ReservationDAO
    Data Access Object for reservation management.

    ReservationDAO.CreateReservationResult

    ReservationFormController
    JavaFX controller for the reservation creation form (popup/window).
    ReservationRow
    Represents a single reservation row displayed in JavaFX TableView components.
    RestaurantTableDAO
    Data Access Object for restaurant table management.
    RestaurantTableDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a restaurant table.
    SceneManager
    Central navigation utility for switching between JavaFX scenes (FXML screens).
    ServerController
    JavaFX controller for the server window (FXML).
    ServerFX
    JavaFX entry point for the Bistro Server application.
    StaffController
    Staff dashboard controller (Agent/Manager) for managing restaurant operations.
    StaffDAO
    Data Access Object for staff management.
    SubscriberDAO
    Data Access Object for subscriber management.
    SubscriberDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a restaurant subscriber.
    SubscriberRow
    JavaFX row-model for displaying Subscriber data in a TableView.
    TerminalActiveItemDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing an active terminal item.
    TerminalController
    Controller for the public terminal screen.
    TerminalEntryController
     
    TerminalValidateResponseDTO
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the response for validating a reservation or waiting list code at the terminal.
    TxtBillImporter
    Imports bill records from a CSV (txt) file into the database.
    TxtOpeningHoursImporter
    Imports opening hours data from a CSV (txt) file into the database.
    TxtPerformanceLogImporter
    Imports performance log records from a CSV (txt) file into the database.
    TxtReservationImporter
    Imports reservation records from a CSV (txt) file into the database.
    TxtRestaurantTableImporter
    Imports restaurant table data from a CSV (txt) file into the database.
    TxtStaffImporter
    Imports staff users from a CSV (txt) file into the staff table.
    TxtSubscriberImporter
    Imports subscribers data from a CSV (txt) file into the subscribers table.
    TxtUserActivityImporter
    Imports user activity records from a CSV (txt) file into the user_activity table.
    TxtVisitImporter
    Imports visit records from a CSV (txt) file into the visit table.
    TxtWaitingListImporter
    Imports waiting list records from a CSV (txt) file into the waiting_list table.
    UserActivityDAO
    Data Access Object for user activity tracking.
    UserActivityDAO.ActiveCodeResult
    Simple holder for an active confirmation code.
    UserActivityDAO.LostCodeResult
    Result holder for lost confirmation-code recovery.
    VisitDAO
    Data Access Object for visit records.
    WaitingListDAO
    Data Access Object for waiting list management.
    WaitingListDTO
    DTO representing a waiting list entry for walk-in customers or subscribers.
    WaitingListRow
    A lightweight table-row model for displaying waiting list entries in JavaFX tables.
